Add Cookie Without Url, Path And Domain
    Run Keyword And Expect Error
    ...    Error: browserContext.addCookies: Cookie should have a url or a domain/path pair
    ...    Add Cookie    Foo    Bar

Add Cookie With Url
    [Tags]    no-windows-support
    ${url} =    Get Url
    Add Cookie    Foo    Bar    url=${url}
    ${cookies} =    Get Cookies
